thread.title: Belinda

author: Belinda
title: Belinda
text: I'm so,thankful for Ticketmaster Resale. I had one ticket to the "hard to get seats" St George Open Air Cinema. But I needed another and the pre sale was sold out. So I had the choice of queing up on the night with hundreds of people in hope to get just one of 40 tickets available at the door, or I buy a ticket from TicketMaster Resale for just a fraction more but for peace of mind, Thankyou Ticketmaster Resale. You are brilliant and I'll be back again and again.
